{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handlePushRegistration:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSData","text":"NSData"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"deviceToken"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"deviceToken","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The device token Data received from APNs"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Call this method from your AppDelegate’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"application:didRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithDeviceToken:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to forward the device token to Pushwoosh."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK normally handles this automatically via method swizzling, but you may need to call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"this directly if:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You’ve disabled swizzling"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You’re managing multiple push providers"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You need custom token processing","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Manual token handling with multiple push providers:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                    didRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithDeviceToken deviceToken: Data) {","","        \/\/ Convert token to string for logging","        let tokenString = deviceToken.map { String(format: \"%02.2hhx\", $0) }.joined()","        Logger.info(\"Received APNs token: \\(tokenString.prefix(20))...\")","","        \/\/ Send to Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistration(deviceToken)","","        \/\/ Send to other push providers if needed","        FirebaseMessaging.messaging().apnsToken = deviceToken","","        \/\/ Sync with backend","        BackendAPI.shared.updatePushToken(tokenString)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Only use this method if you need manual control.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistration:"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Manually handles the device push token registration.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","title":"handlePushRegistration:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handlePushRegistration:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistration:"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistration:"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistration:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"role":"collection","title":"Pushw